Different categories of spells make the weapon do different things. This effect will overlay on top of normal enchants and does include additional weapon FX that will overlay too. It even works on Bound weapons.

Retexture of the wood chest into a common simple viking middle age chest.



Plans for the future: make a variant with iron viking decorations.

State.Author: NsJones
State.Description:
NEW: Now with glowing eye textures.

This mod aims to make werewolves more brutal and aggressive by making them sound like savage beasts they are supposed to be, with 3 different sound overhaul versions to choose from.

Now also with werewolf body and eye textures and an optional speed upgrade, and a skyrim video series I made.
State.Name: Heart of the Beast - Werewolf Sound and Texture Overhaul

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: The Ancient Nordic Sentinels are a type of gigantic Foundation Stone Golem made of old norse architecture. Guardians of the ancient tombs, and the terror of their invaders, these fearsome colossi animated by the souls of powerful warriors will crush all foes with no mercy.
State.Name: Ancient Nordic Sentinel- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: On ancient ages, when neither the Blades had appeared yet, groups of annonymous honorable and strong men raised their weapons against the tyranny of dragons, when almost all still saw them as mighty gods to be venerated. This men are bound in destiny with dragons and with this last ones returning, their past slayers are coming back again too.
State.Name: Ancient Skeletons- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: The Ash Golem is a refined, brute-like, extremely powerfull variant of an Ash Guardian, and user of a big sort of ash based spells. They're originally made with a chest belt containing a heart stone, what prevents the risk of going unbound.
State.Name: Ash Golem- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mharlek1
State.Description:
The ultimate mod package for the beast races boasting thousands of possible outcomes for player character creation with exciting new vanilla based models accompanied by a complete npc replacer for all Argonians and Khajiit, named npcs and leveled lists, with glorious reimagining.

And beyond: optional unique npc replacer addons for other mods
State.Name: BeastHHBB - Khajiit and Argonian content - player character and NPC replacer

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Minotaurs are a powerfull beast-race with physical features of both man and bull. The forest dweller cyrodilic ones are the most degenerated descendants of Morihaus and the now extinct Alessian Empire's minotaur civilization. This variant is feral, and bulkier than their Skyrim's cousins, but use more primitive armoury.
State.Name: Cyrodilic Minotaurs - Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail- SoN6of6TrediS- Amin Khani- ex0tekk
State.Description: The dark art of Necromancy holds many sources of immense power for those who go into it bravely enough to become true Necromasters. Among them, the transformation into a horrifying Bone Tyrant is perhaps the ability that offers greater physical power to a necromancer.
State.Name: Bone Tyrants- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Cockatrices are big flying chimeras resembling a draconic rooster or chicken, created by powerfull alchemists. The process is clouded in mistery, but is known that they born of eggs laid by roosters consorting with roosters, then the egg must be incubated by a toad or snake, which is devoured by the beast when he hatches.
State.Name: Cockatrices- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Cthulhoids are robust vaguely humanoid daedra with greenish warty skin, having as main characteristic a disturbing head that resembles that of an octopus, with tentacles coming out of the chin, and a mouth full of several rows of sharp teeth. Poisonous, their bodies produce a constant toxic secretion.
State.Name: Cthulhoids- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: yousukeve
State.Description: This MOD changes the standing animation for dragons.
State.Name: Dragon Animation Replace in Special Edition

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Also known as Helhests, these mummified undead horses were the mounts of the ancient Norse, now resurrected by the same kind of power that keeps their former masters awake.
State.Name: Draugr Horse Mount- Mihail Monsters and Animals (SE-AE version)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Add roaming exterior Draugr patrols to Skyrim with this mod. This patrols of undead merciless pillagers descend from their ancient nordic tombs into the roads at night, followed by their undead hounds, in search for clutter and fresh food to be used on their daily ritualistic dungeon tasks.
State.Name: Draugr Patrols - Mihail Monsters and Animals  (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Ettins are abominations with two-heads and an immense fury for all living beings. Descendants of an ogre tribe cursed by Malacath himself in remote ages, these tormented beasts of incredible strength, but limited intellect, are all that an adventurer does not want to encounter.
State.Name: Ettins - Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Centaurs are an ancient and mysterious sentient beast-race, with traits of men and horse. Alternatively worshipped and despised, legends of their exploits range from the epic to the pornographic. The Council of Artaeum have called the Centaurs "true followers of the Old Ways" of Tamriel, but the true meaning of that is unknown.
State.Name: Centaurs- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Name: Fashions Of The Banditry- A bandit-focused Armor Pack (CBBE-3BA-HIMBO)

State.Author: tktk
State.Description:
To transform faster human to werewolf or werebear or vampire lord.

"Quick" omit transforming animation as short as possible. "Half" is twice as fast as the vanilla transforming animation.

This mod does not have script and esp. It only is changed animations.
State.Name: Faster Transform - To Werewolf and VampireLord

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Compilation of all of Mihail's Giant mods in one esp. Finally the Giant family will be complete in your game, bringing immersion and realism to their kind, and filling a lore gap that has existed for over 10 years.
State.Name: Female Giants and Younglings- Mihail Monsters and Animals (SE-AE version)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Fiendroths are small, generally harmless daedric beetles that reach Nirn through the residual energy used in summoning more powerful daedra, and that become pests wherever they occur.
State.Name: Fiendroth Beetles- Mihail Monsters and Animals (SE-AE version)

State.Author: Afrotoast
State.Description: A massive creature and gameplay overhaul to make Skyrim more grim and unpredictable.
State.Name: Rogue-Like Encounters SSE - Savage North Overhaul

State.Author: NickNak Maxsu
State.Description:
A little mod that allows the player and npcs to flinch when hit

This version uses the OnHitFramework for hit detection
State.Name: Flinching - Script Free Edition

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Now you can ride a legendary Snow-elf's Frost Mare, made of the purest ice and adorned with the finest ivory, or the bizarre Ice-Carved Steed, a construct animated by rudimentary riekling magic, mimicking the Frost Mares and that will surely give your gameplay a unique tone of surreality.
State.Name: Frost Coursers- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Giant snakes are large and extremely poisonous reptiles, that occasionally eat small boats and were rarely seen on land. Widely hunted, today their numbers have reduced, and so have their size, but they are still dangerous enemies and the terror of any unwary adventurer, that they manage to ambush , with their slithering cunning.
State.Name: Giant Snakes - Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Goblins are violent and primitive small orc-kin humanoids found throughout Tamriel, often living in sewers, caves, cluttered camps and ruins, in small clan-based societies. Accompanied by their tamed Durzogs, they are known for making their camps near roads to rob travelers. Goblins are sentient, and worship Malacath.
State.Name: Goblins- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Hand made animations that completely overhaul Skyrim's 3rd person enchanted staff playstyles, designed to work with hybrid playstyles as well (staff+melee or staff+spell), requires DAR.
State.Name: Goetia Animations - Enchanted Staves

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Gorgonops are agile small reptomammals, with powerfull large jaws and teeth. Two species inhabit skyrim, the smaller spotted Lycaenops, that hunts in packs on the tundra, with the size of a small fox, and the solitary Gorgonops, bigger, and only seem on the volcanic area of Eastmarsh.
State.Name: Gorgonops - Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Materialized from obscure childhood fears, what could be more frightening than a profound trauma turned into a solid, horrifying form of flesh and blood, which returns from the past forgotten in time, to torment those who try to forget it at all costs?
State.Name: Grey Children- Mihail Monsters and Animals (SE-AE version)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: The Griffin is a big flying apex predator native from High Rock, Hammerfell and Skyrim. He looks like a combination of a ferocious lion and a giant eagle. It usually inhabits primeval highlands and builds its nests on unreachable mountain summits, some also occur on the desert areas of Craglorn.
State.Name: Griffins- Mihail Monsters and Animals (SE-AE version)

State.Author: Araanim
State.Description: The Sea of Ghosts, they call it. An emptiness of ice and fog, lifeless and haunted. But the icy depths hide horrors even the Dragonborn has never faced. Legends tell of the beasts that dwell in the deep.  Monsters of such immensity, that even the dragons fear them. And now, like the dragons, the monsters have awoken...
State.Name: Here There Be Monsters SSE

State.Author: TheRetroCarrot
State.Description: This improves the Draw/Sheathe sounds for use in VR.

State.Name: Improved Eyes Skyrim

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Indriks are feathered magical deer-like creatures that bear some direct relation to Y'ffre. Indriks fight using elemental-based attacks, with power drawn from the very Earth Bones beneath their hooves. Relentless protectors of nature, a wild Indrik will not hesitate to slaughter anyone he deems to be a potential danger to nature.
State.Name: Indrik- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Mimics are one of the strangest daedra of Sheogorath. They disguise themselves as chests, waiting for victims to try to open them. When a victim attempts to do so, Mimics will proceed to reveal their dread true form and attack chomping her with their enormous mouth filled with pointed teeth and tearing skin with their long arms with sharp claws.
State.Name: Mimics- Mihail Monsters and Animas (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Compilation of all of Mihail's Minotaur mods in one esp. The forests will never be the same, now patrolled by these fierce bull-men, descendants of the demigod Morihaus
State.Name: Minotaurs - Mihail Monsters and Animals (SE-AE version)

State.Author: Laup26
State.Description: Bard, Hunter, Big Game, Traveler and Knight Saddles for all explorers and adventurers. Get off your feet, take up the reins and aim for the horizon. Nothing can stop you when you and your trusty stead are ready for it all. More Saddles brings you four more saddles to further customize your horse for the journeys ahead.
State.Name: More Saddles SSE - Horse

State.Author: XxTWDxX
State.Description: Modifies the default death sounds of NPCs to make them sound more painful.

State.Name: Pixies- Mihail Monsters and Animals (SE-AE version)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Small and pesky lesser daedras, of little intelligence and cowardly behavior, with modest magical abilities, scamps and banekins should not be, at first sight, a matter of concern for prepared adventurers, however, in large numbers these two species can be a nuisance even for the most fearless warriors.
State.Name: Scamps and Banekins- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Description: Adds sunlight and shadows to some small exterior world spaces that lacked sunlight: Shalidor's Maze, Giant's Grove, and Castle Volkihar Courtyard
State.Name: Shadows Of Sunlight - In Small Exterior World Spaces

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: What could be more frightening than a vampire, than his bloody skeletal remains reanimated as irrational killing machines with an uncontrollable bloodlust? These fearless skeletons will freeze your spine when you find them patrolling the darkest of the dungeons.
State.Name: Skeletal Vampires- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: lifestorock and jackstarr
State.Description: Skyrim Immersive Creatures adds dozens of new creatures to enhance your gaming experience. This mod adds brand new creatures which fit in to the world of Skyrim, alongside variations of existing creatures, adding diversity and improving gameplay.
State.Name: Skyrim Immersive Creatures Special Edition

Original.Name: Sleeping Expanded - Animations and NPC Reactions-59250-1-21-1658913240.rar

State.Author: JaySerpa
State.Description: Ever noticed how NPCs don't react at all to being woken up in the middle of the night? Or how characters stop breathing while they sleep? Or... how it takes them YEARS to get in and out of bed? Well, no more! WAKE UP, JARL BALGRUUF!!!!!!! Sleeping Expanded is here!!!!
State.Name: Sleeping Expanded - Animations and NPC reactions

State.Author: cunny1975
State.Description: A 4K or optional 2K retexture of the SMIM large chest found in ruins.

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: First appeared on TES: Shadowkey, Snowrays are flying bluish- purple manta rays and one of the ancient and now rare original strange fauna of Skyrim, prior to the arrival of the nords, giants and other creatures from Atmora. They live in small roaming shoals accross the snowhills of north skyrim and their stingers produce a blood freezing poison.
State.Name: Snowrays- Mihail Monsters and Animal (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Thri-Kreen are mutated ritualistic warriors created by falmer alchemy using the Chaurus as a base. These obedient humanoid insects outperform the own Falmers in physical capacities, and do not need to rest, being excellent defenders of the hives where they live, despite having limited intelligence, just like any other Chaurus.
State.Name: Thri-Kreen Warriors - Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Fridam

State.Description: A Fully Voiced Sound FX Rework to Dragon Priests
State.Name: Valthume - Dragon Priest Voiced Sound Rework -

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: All types of Vampire beasts are commonly considered lesser vampires, but this description can be deceiving, for lesser does not mean weak and stupid. True, they are primitive and bear a closer relation to animals than to humans, but when they drop on their prey from above, they can be just as dangerous as their more noble cousins
State.Name: Vampire Beasts- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: StickySock
State.Description: Inspired by  "Simple Night Spawner", this mod was made to encompass a variety of scary and disturbing monsters from popular mod authors in an attempt to make traversing the world at night as horrifying as possible.
State.Name: SNS - Scary Night Spawner

State.Author: mashanen jasperthegnome
State.Description: Softer Salt & Wind textures for vanilla hairs - no .esp, textures only, should work with LE
State.Name: Vanilla hair - Salt and Wind

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: House Cats are docile small felines, used as pets by nords on the cities, also to make rodent control on farms and inns. They are ambient animals, and will not engage in combat.
State.Name: House Cats- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Pigeons are gentle, plump, small-billed birds with a skin saddle (cere) between the bill and forehead, that live commonly in human settlements, eating the remains of food, specially bread and grain, left behind by the city inhabitants.
State.Name: Pigeons- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Wolfman5750 Nyphani GroLak2020
State.Description: A body for werewolves(or werebears) in VR! Also enables compatibility of your installed modded werewolf/werebear textures for use in 1st person!
State.Name: Werewolf Body for VR

State.Description: Attempts to update complimentary meshes to those modified by ELFX, created by anamorfus.
